-- Boards of Hyundai Motor affiliates approve signing of $10 bln land deal
-- By Hyunjoo Jin
-- Fri Sep 26, 2014 12:52AM EDT
-- None



SEOUL, Sept 26 (Reuters) - The boards of Hyundai Motor Co <005380.KS> and two affiliates on Friday approved the signing of their 10.55 trillion won ($10.12 billion) deal to buy a plot of land in Seoul valued at about a third of that amount, the companies said.

